g.text: Assessment of Socio-Economic and Climate Change Impacts on
Water Resources in Four European Lagoon Catchments
Received: 4 September 2018 / Accepted: 18 July 2019 / Published online: 8 November 2019
This study demonstrates the importance of considering potential land use and management changes in climate impact
research. By taking into account possible trends of economic development and environmental awareness, we assess effects
of global warming on water availability and quality in the catchments of four European lagoons:
